{[%mdl 8192] A29: English Opening: Four Knights Variation with 4 g3} 1. c4 e5 2. Nc3 Nf6 3. g3 Bb4 4. Bg2 O-O 5. Nf3 Re8 6. O-O Nc6 7. Nd5 Bf8 8. d3 h6 9. b3 d6 10. Bb2 Nxd5 11. cxd5 Ne7 12. e4 c5 13. dxc6 Nxc6 14. d4 {last book move.} Bg4 15. d5 {White threatens to win material: d5xc6} Ne7 16. Qd3 Qd7 17. Nd2 {Black's piece can't move: f8} Bh3 18. a4 Bxg2 19. Kxg2 Reb8 20. Nc4 b5 21. axb5 Qxb5 22. Ra3 Ng6 23. Rfa1 a6 24. Bc1 Rb7 25. Be3 f6 26. f3 Ne7 27. Qf1 Nc8 28. Nd2 Qb4 29. Qc4 Qxc4 30. Nxc4 Rab8 31. Nd2 Rc7 32. Rxa6 Rc2 33. R6a2 Rxa2 34. Rxa2 Be7 35. Kf2 Kf7 36. Ke2 Ke8 37. Kd3 Kd7 38. Kc3 Bd8 39. Nc4 Bc7 40. g4 Bd8 41. Ra6 Bc7 42. h4 Bd8 43. h5 Bc7 44. b4 Rb7 (44... Ne7 {is not the saving move} 45. Ba7 Rb7 46. Bb6 Bxb6 47. Nxb6+ Kd8 48. Nc4 $18) 45. Ra8 Kd8 46. Kb3 Rb8 (46... Kd7 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} 47. Ka4 $18) 47. Rxb8 Bxb8 48. b5 Ne7 49. b6 f5 (49... Kd7 {hardly improves anything} 50. Kb4 $18) 50. gxf5 Ng8 51. Bf2 Nf6 52. Bh4 (52. Bh4 Ke8 53. Bxf6 Kf7 54. Na5 Kxf6 55. Nc6 Kg5 56. Nxb8 Kf4 57. b7 Ke3 58. Nc6 Kf4 59. b8=Q Ke3 60. Qxd6 Ke2 61. Qxe5 g5 62. hxg6 Ke3 63. g7 Kd2 64. Qb2+ Ke3 65. g8=Q Kf4 66. Qd2+ Kxf3 67. Qgg2#) 1-0


