45. Rxc4+ $1 {This surprising sacrifice leads to a decisive material advantage. 45...} Kxc4 ({After} 45... bxc4 46. Nc2+ {White also wins a piece.}) 46. Nd2+ {Both the available king moves walk into a knight fork. 46...} Kd4 47. Nb3+ Ke3 48. Nxd5+ exd5 49. Nxa1 {Black has no chance since White is a piece and a pawn ahead. 49...} Kd2 50. Nb3+ Ke3 51. h4 g6 52. Kg3 Kd3 53. Kf4 Kc4 54. Nc1 1-0


